## 7. Integration Points & Contracts

### 7.1 HTTP API Contract (locked at end of Task 1+4)

**`POST /api/chat`**
- Request: `Content-Type: application/json` — `{ "prompt": string }`
- Response 200: `{ "response": string, "agentType": "weather" | "research" | "other" }`
- Response 400: `{ "error": string }` — empty/missing prompt
- Response 500: `{ "error": string }` — orchestrator/API failure

**`GET /`** → `public/index.html` (served by `express.static`)

**`GET /*` (any static file)** → served from `public/` if present, else 404

### 7.2 Import graph after Sprint 4
```
server.ts
  ├── agent/orchestrator.ts (→ runAgent, runResearchAgent)
  └── config/env.ts (side-effect boot validation)
```

`index.ts` removed. No circular imports introduced.

### 7.3 Env & runtime contract
- Node ≥18 required (already in `engines` field)
- `.env` must contain `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` — validated at boot
- Port 5002 must be free on `npm run dev` / `npm start`
- `public/` must exist at project root (not inside `dist/` or `src/`)

